Added per-client ChannelMode (.stereo/.leftChannel/.rightChannel/.muted) applied at AudioPlayer de-interleave so two Macs can act as L+R speakers of a stereo pair, plus 1s scheduler counters in ClientSession.handleAudioPacket (rxCount/schedCount/dropNotLocked/dropPast) to localize the still-no-audio symptom — feature + diagnostic in one pass since they touch the same code path.